Subject: a classy metonymy?
Status: R


On a recent America West flight, I was given a napkin with a "System Route Map"
printed on it. The mapkin bore the following caveat:

 "Cities served by America West Airlines are subject to change without notice."


Were we on a bombing raid, I wondered ...

Yours metonymically,

John



